{"tid":2375643,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《GTA5》麥可配音演員確診武漢肺炎","createTime":"2021-01-22T07:35:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T11:18:36.000Z","uid":199496,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"eb0ff71ce4d38165ac40b3f633df499ca6954bc6","tid":2375643,"uid":199496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:35:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DTwo0NB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDTwo0NB.jpg&h=427d046d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在《俠盜獵車手 V》（Grand Theft Auto V／GTA5）中飾演與配音主角之一麥可&middot;湯利（Michael Townley）的 Ned Luke，近日在 Twitter 上表示自己武漢肺炎確診，表示感染武漢肺炎並不好受，但自己會像以前一樣堅強起來，同時稱讚前線的醫護人員是真正的英雄。<br />\n<br />\nNed Luke 在 Twitter 上貼出了自己住院中的照片，表示自己因為患上武漢肺炎，被送到了醫院進行治療。這讓他得好好休養一段時間，但他會盡快恢復，並感謝所有粉絲們的支持，也謝謝那些在一線的醫護與人員，希望大家多多支持他們。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ned_luke/status/1350550169046163464?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fned_luke%2Fstatus%2F1350550169046163464%3Fs%3D20&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4Ter6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=f182bb07\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fned_luke%2Fstatus%2F1350550169046163464%3Fs%3D20&h=17e1e143\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ned_luke/status/1350550169046163464?s=20</a><br />\n&ldquo;昨天我因為武漢肺炎被送進了 Emory John&rsquo;s Creek 醫院。這是真的，而且很不好受。我會休息一陣子，但我很快就會像以往一樣堅強的回歸。保重也感謝支持。前線的醫療人員是真正的英雄，支持他們！&rdquo;"},{"pid":"a335737b1306a878563284d87caa41f5438bc419","tid":2375643,"uid":199496,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:36:10.000Z","msg":"已出院<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ned_luke/status/1351713887255670784?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fned_luke%2Fstatus%2F1351713887255670784%3Fs%3D21&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4Ter6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=906ca0b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fned_luke%2Fstatus%2F1351713887255670784%3Fs%3D21&h=b27a54c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ned_luke/status/1351713887255670784?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"1343ca65ff6284e26704d53c64f228b32c27ce47","tid":2375643,"uid":38904,"like":4,"dislike":12,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:36:39.000Z","msg":"又真係幾似michael <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"611835728730717abfb8d33c87e27fb1411658f1","tid":2375643,"uid":228894,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:39:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/21lMY8FNots\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F21lMY8FNots&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4Ter6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=013fe70b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/21lMY8FNots</a><br />\n麥可！！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cb5a1bf4fbf49393915ee847c392664552be971","tid":2375643,"uid":24660,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:39:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://as.com/meristation/imagenes/2018/11/13/noticias/1542118504_058770_1542118551_noticia_normal.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fas.com%2Fmeristation%2Fimagenes%2F2018%2F11%2F13%2Fnoticias%2F1542118504_058770_1542118551_noticia_normal.jpg&h=46366195&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7d0137258a0e5d7ee2c814b99f165de696f54967","tid":2375643,"uid":218684,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:39:34.000Z","msg":"You forget a thousand things every day, make sure this is one of them."},{"pid":"8714ccb305890886e3e7fb5b15c165739524e1bd","tid":2375643,"uid":60488,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"1343ca65ff6284e26704d53c64f228b32c27ce47","tid":2375643,"uid":38904,"like":4,"dislike":12,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:36:39.000Z","msg":"又真係幾似michael <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:40